JIRA currently uses SAL 2.1.0.  It would be more useful in cross-product plugin development if JIRA used SAL 2.2.0 or higher.

As an example, SAL 2.2.0 exposes the user profile in the [UserManager|http://docs.atlassian.com/sal-api/2.3.1/sal-api/apidocs/com/atlassian/sal/api/user/UserManager.html].  Without this, there isn't a product-independent way of determining the current user's email address.

